M|Cont|tx|nt is the **second ag** in the CSE pipeline. Runs after ka's brief, before ln's pitch writing.
M|CSE |tx|```
M|CSE |tx|Score = (EГ—0.25) + (RГ—0.25) + (GГ—0.20) + (BГ—0.15) + (TГ—0.15)
M|CSE |Mini|45
M|CSE |tx|```
M|CSE |tx|\| Factor \| Weight \| What it measures \|
M|CSE |tx|\|---\|---\|---\|
M|CSE |tx|\| E вЂ” Engagement Signal \| 25% \| How strong is the engagement signal from an/cr data \|
M|CSE |tx|\| R вЂ” Recency/tn \| 25% \| How aligned is the idea w/ current trending formats/topics \|
M|CSE |tx|\| G вЂ” Gap Opportunity \| 20% \| How large and unclaimed is the mk gap \|
M|CSE |tx|\| B вЂ” br Fit \| 15% \| How well does this fit the vt's voice and positioning \|
M|CSE |tx|\| T вЂ” Timing Urgency \| 15% \| How time-sensitive is this window (URGENCY_WINDOW = hi T) \|
